mary":"Robert Cumberworth(이)가 대략 1332년 영국 링코실르에서 태어났을 때, 그의 아버지 Robert Cumberworth(은)는 40세였고, 그의 어머니 Mrs Robert Cumberworth(은)는 40세였다. 그는 1357년 영국 잉글랜드 요르크실르 이스트 리딩 플램루그h에서 Sibil Erghum(와)과 결혼했다. 그들은 적어도 한 명의 아들과 한 명의 딸을 두었다. 그는 1404년 7월 15일 이후 영국 잉글랜드 링코실르 서머비에서 사망했으며 영국 잉글랜드 링코실르 서머비에 묻혔다."},"lv":{"1332–Aft 15 July 1404":"ap 1332. gadu–pēc 1404. gada 15. jūlija","1332–1404":"ap1332.gadu–1404","1340–1408":"1340–1408","1365–1404":"1365–1404","1370–1426":"1370.gads–1426","1293–1405":"1293–1405","1293–Female":"1293–mirusi","Aft 15 July 1404":"pēc 1404. gada 15. jūlija","after 15 July 1404":"pēc 1404. gada 15. jūlija","1340":"1340","Abt 1335":"ap 1335. gadu","1382":"1382","1370":"1370. gads","1293":"1293","1426":"1426","1404":"1404","1337":"1337","1357":"1357. gads","about 1404":"ap 1404. gadu","1332":"ap 1332. gadu","1453":"1453","1365":"1365","about 1365":"ap 1365. gadu","1408":"1408","1405":"1405","Somerby, Lincolnshire, England":"Somerby, Lincolnshire, Anglija, Lielbritānija","Flamborough, Yorkshire, England":"Flamborough, Yorkshire East Riding, Anglija, Lielbritānija","England":"England","Lincolnshire, England":"Lincolnshire, England"},"mg":{"1332–Aft 15 July 1404":"tany ho any amin'ny 1332–taorian'ny 15 jolay 1404","1332–1404":"tanyhoanyamin'ny1332–1404","1340–1408":"1340–1408","1365–1404":"1365–1404","1370–1426":"1370–1426","1293–1405":"1293–1405","1293–Female":"1293–Maty","Aft 15 July 1404":"taorian'ny 15 jolay 1404","after 15 July 1404":"taorian'ny 15 jolay 1404","1340":"1340","Abt 1335":"tany ho any amin'ny 1335","1382":"1382","1370":"1370","1293":"1293","1426":"1426","1404":"1404","1337":"1337","1357":"1357","about 1404":"tany ho any amin'ny 1404","1332":"tany ho any amin'ny 1332","1453":"1453","1365":"1365","about 1365":"tany ho any amin'ny 1365","1408":"1408","1405":"1405","Somerby, Lincolnshire, England":"Somerby, Lincolnshire, Angletera, United Kingdom","Flamborough, Yorkshire, England":"Flamborough, Yorkshire East Riding, Angletera, United Kingdom","Eng